Dad, time for your medicine.

00:30:03.361 --> 00:30:04.000
No.

00:30:04.881 --> 00:30:05.601
I don't take it.

00:30:07.681 --> 00:30:09.080
If you don't take your medicine,

00:30:09.320 --> 00:30:11.480
your head will hurt tomorrow morning.

00:30:11.480 --> 00:30:12.201
No.

00:30:13.080 --> 00:30:14.240
Be good, take one pill.

00:30:15.240 --> 00:30:16.000
- Here.
- No.

00:30:16.280 --> 00:30:17.040
Just one.

00:30:17.040 --> 00:30:18.121
You want to kill me?

00:30:19.121 --> 00:30:19.921
Do you?

00:30:21.560 --> 00:30:22.681
Don't think I don't know.

00:30:22.681 --> 00:30:24.401
You're with them.

00:30:25.240 --> 00:30:26.921
You implanted a chip in my brain

00:30:26.921 --> 00:30:27.921
and set up an antenna!

00:30:29.641 --> 00:30:31.201
Talking to me day and night.

00:30:31.361 --> 00:30:32.401
Won't even let me sleep.

00:30:32.401 --> 00:30:33.560
Just trying to kill me!

00:30:33.560 --> 00:30:34.401
Medicine?

00:30:34.921 --> 00:30:36.520
What for?

00:30:37.040 --> 00:30:38.040
Is this medicine?

00:30:40.480 --> 00:30:41.401
Is this medicine?

00:30:42.040 --> 00:30:43.240
It's a battery.

00:30:44.000 --> 00:30:44.520
Medicine?

00:30:44.841 --> 00:30:46.681
Why let me take medicine?

00:30:46.800 --> 00:30:47.441
You!

00:30:51.240 --> 00:30:51.921
Take it.

00:30:53.681 --> 00:30:55.240
Take it.

00:30:56.320 --> 00:30:58.320
Come in, all of you!

00:30:58.601 --> 00:30:59.841
You're all evil.

00:31:05.772 --> 00:31:11.256
(Incoming Video Call
Son)

