(No-Name Diner)

00:33:18.411 --> 00:33:22.648
(No-Name Diner)

00:33:22.648 --> 00:33:29.432
(Tasty Dishes, Home-style)

00:33:41.441 --> 00:33:42.080
Careful!

00:33:42.401 --> 00:33:43.080
Come on.

00:33:48.921 --> 00:33:49.560
Anything else?

00:33:49.760 --> 00:33:50.320
That's all.

00:33:55.520 --> 00:33:56.201
(No-Name Diner)
Bye.

00:33:56.201 --> 00:33:57.441
- Bye.
- Bye.

00:33:58.280 --> 00:33:58.961
See you tomorrow.

00:33:59.921 --> 00:34:01.000
Thank you, Lei.

00:34:03.052 --> 00:34:07.160
(No-Name Diner)

00:34:08.024 --> 00:34:08.600
Ma'am.

00:34:08.600 --> 00:34:10.008
- Here to send us food?
- Yes.

00:34:10.008 --> 00:34:11.480
Today's stir-fried tomato and egg.

00:34:11.480 --> 00:34:12.080
Looks great!

00:34:12.080 --> 00:34:13.361
Can I take one more?

00:34:13.361 --> 00:34:14.441
Sure, no problem.

00:34:14.441 --> 00:34:15.600
And water, here.

00:34:15.881 --> 00:34:16.520
Here you go.

00:34:16.721 --> 00:34:17.401
Thanks.

00:34:17.401 --> 00:34:18.441
Careful, don't spill it.

00:34:18.441 --> 00:34:19.241
Take it easy.

00:34:19.241 --> 00:34:20.520
- Thanks!
- Come get more if you need.

00:34:22.401 --> 00:34:23.600
I'll take this to Ms. Zhang.

00:34:24.361 --> 00:34:25.321
- Here you go.
- Thanks.

00:34:25.321 --> 00:34:26.160
Rough day today.

00:34:27.321 --> 00:34:27.841
Thanks.

00:34:28.241 --> 00:34:28.761
Water.

00:34:30.480 --> 00:34:31.224
What's for today?

00:34:31.321 --> 00:34:32.120
Tomato and egg.

00:34:32.120 --> 00:34:32.640
Ma'am.

00:34:32.640 --> 00:34:33.241
Cucumber...

00:34:33.241 --> 00:34:33.841
Your meal.

00:34:33.841 --> 00:34:34.520
- Thanks.
- Not at all.

00:34:34.520 --> 00:34:35.321
Please sit.

00:34:36.160 --> 00:34:36.921
You're too kind.

00:34:36.921 --> 00:34:37.721
I'll open it.

00:34:38.000 --> 00:34:39.241
No. I got it myself.

00:34:39.241 --> 00:34:40.241
Your leg hurting again?

00:34:40.241 --> 00:34:42.120
Yes. It's an old problem.

00:34:42.120 --> 00:34:42.921
- Old problem.
- It's fine.

00:34:44.120 --> 00:34:45.361
I'll bring you some medicine.

00:34:45.480 --> 00:34:46.160
Thanks.

00:34:46.160 --> 00:34:47.801
How's the taste? Enough to eat?

00:34:48.000 --> 00:34:49.000
- Good.
- Take your time.

00:35:05.200 --> 00:35:06.200
Your cooking skills

00:35:06.480 --> 00:35:07.560
are really amazing!

00:35:09.640 --> 00:35:10.600
To be honest,

00:35:10.600 --> 00:35:12.401
this is the moment I enjoy most
every week.

00:35:12.401 --> 00:35:13.961
Sit here and properly have a meal.

00:35:15.241 --> 00:35:16.961
I loved eating since I was a kid,

00:35:17.441 --> 00:35:18.480
so I wanted to open

00:35:18.480 --> 00:35:20.361
a restaurant and become a chef
when I grow up.

00:35:21.401 --> 00:35:22.841
That'd be comfortable.

00:35:22.841 --> 00:35:23.961
But my parents objected.

00:35:25.000 --> 00:35:26.441
They thought it was too exhausting

00:35:26.441 --> 00:35:28.120
and wanted me to get an easier job.

00:35:28.120 --> 00:35:30.552
It doesn't matter if I can earn much,
as long as I was happy.

00:35:30.881 --> 00:35:32.120
Now, I become a policeman

00:35:32.680 --> 00:35:33.961
and realize it's exhausting too.

00:35:37.841 --> 00:35:39.256
Are you happy being a policeman?

00:35:42.000 --> 00:35:43.361
Yes. What about you?

00:36:04.075 --> 00:36:06.744
(Captain Office)

00:36:15.560 --> 00:36:16.200
Come in.

00:36:23.200 --> 00:36:24.961
Captain Leng, I'm Ye Qian.

00:36:25.000 --> 00:36:26.560
The division asked me to come to you.

00:36:26.892 --> 00:36:29.016
(Exemplary Unit
Collective Second-Class Merit)

00:36:31.881 --> 00:36:33.921
How much is this watch?

00:36:37.961 --> 00:36:39.361
Sir, I don't know.

00:36:40.961 --> 00:36:42.401
You don't know?

00:36:43.480 --> 00:36:45.281
I'm asking how much this watch is.

00:36:45.881 --> 00:36:46.721
Captain Leng,

00:36:47.200 --> 00:36:49.160
it's a birthday gift from someone.

00:36:49.160 --> 00:36:51.200
- I don't...
- I didn't ask who gave it to you.

00:36:51.401 --> 00:36:53.401
I'm asking how much this watch is.

00:36:55.520 --> 00:36:56.321
If you don't know,

00:36:56.520 --> 00:36:57.600
go back to your division.

00:36:58.040 --> 00:36:59.200
There's no work for you here.

00:37:00.600 --> 00:37:02.080
No, I'm not going back.

00:37:02.801 --> 00:37:04.640
I join your unit to catch criminals.

00:37:04.801 --> 00:37:05.721
Catch every single one.

00:37:12.401 --> 00:37:13.761
In your division,

00:37:14.080 --> 00:37:15.600
the case-solving rate is 90 percent.

00:37:16.560 --> 00:37:18.680
Sometimes you even
steal cases from our unit.

00:37:19.401 --> 00:37:20.721
That was you, wasn't it?

00:37:22.680 --> 00:37:23.401
Yes.

00:37:26.721 --> 00:37:27.761
Fearless in crisis.

00:37:27.761 --> 00:37:28.961
You suit here.

00:37:29.480 --> 00:37:31.160
Welcome to Major Crimes Unit.

00:37:33.241 --> 00:37:35.600
I was just messing with you earlier.

00:37:36.560 --> 00:37:39.160
There are many criminals
waiting for your arrest.

00:37:40.200 --> 00:37:41.600
You've come to the right place.

00:37:44.241 --> 00:37:45.721
That's your spot over there. Go.

00:37:50.961 --> 00:37:52.120
I heard from Captain Leng

00:37:54.000 --> 00:37:55.928
your family was well-off
when you were young.

00:37:57.120 --> 00:37:58.761
Generally speaking, someone like you

00:37:59.441 --> 00:38:00.961
rarely becomes a criminal policeman.

00:38:05.200 --> 00:38:06.080
Because of her?

00:38:10.921 --> 00:38:14.680
You know Little Zhao's been
waiting for you, right?

00:38:15.200 --> 00:38:16.961
I've made things clear
with her about this.

00:38:20.721 --> 00:38:21.520
Qian.

00:38:24.241 --> 00:38:25.721
Do you have even the slightest

00:38:27.120 --> 00:38:29.040
thought about trying to accept her?

00:38:29.361 --> 00:38:30.080
No.

00:38:32.761 --> 00:38:33.401
Alright.

00:38:34.520 --> 00:38:36.480
Love really can't be forced.

00:38:37.304 --> 00:38:40.441
You love her, yet she doesn't love you.
She loves you, yet you don't love her.

00:38:40.520 --> 00:38:41.841
Can you just eat?

00:38:44.160 --> 00:38:44.841
Alright.

00:39:02.680 --> 00:39:03.841
I'll go to Han Zhao tomorrow.

00:39:05.080 --> 00:39:05.801
Wait,

00:39:06.520 --> 00:39:08.120
you said you have no feelings to her.

00:39:08.120 --> 00:39:09.441
Why do you go to her again?

00:39:22.480 --> 00:39:23.281
Little Qian.

00:39:24.480 --> 00:39:25.961
Where's your little shadow today?

00:39:26.600 --> 00:39:27.441
I'm working.

00:39:28.680 --> 00:39:30.961
You could just call me
to ask about the motorcycle.

00:39:31.040 --> 00:39:32.480
Why bother coming here?

00:39:32.961 --> 00:39:33.761
Missed me?

00:39:35.120 --> 00:39:36.241
This is important.

00:39:36.241 --> 00:39:37.361
Better talked in person.

00:39:38.120 --> 00:39:39.600
Alright. What is it?

00:39:40.520 --> 00:39:42.000
You know the motorcycle circle

00:39:42.000 --> 00:39:42.881
in Wannan, right?

00:39:43.401 --> 00:39:45.480
Any way to track down this motorcycle?

00:39:48.281 --> 00:39:49.801
Dayang DY150.

00:39:49.801 --> 00:39:50.881
Most common model.

00:39:52.281 --> 00:39:53.401
Not easy to find.

00:39:54.480 --> 00:39:56.080
But those stickers are pretty unique.

00:39:56.281 --> 00:39:57.480
If they're all peeled off,

00:39:57.480 --> 00:39:59.544
it's just like any other motorcycle
on the street.

00:40:00.321 --> 00:40:01.721
This is secondhand,

00:40:02.040 --> 00:40:03.040
not well maintained.

00:40:03.080 --> 00:40:04.401
Might even have an oil leak.

00:40:04.841 --> 00:40:07.281
Oil leak? That's great.

00:40:07.448 --> 00:40:09.401
If all the oil leaks out,
the engine will seize,

00:40:09.401 --> 00:40:10.401
then it'll need repairs.

00:40:12.080 --> 00:40:13.680
Send me
its vehicle identification number

00:40:14.000 --> 00:40:15.080
and engine number.

00:40:15.480 --> 00:40:16.560
I'll spread the word.

00:40:21.281 --> 00:40:22.080
A friend of mine

00:40:22.080 --> 00:40:24.040
deals in used motorcycle parts.

00:40:24.040 --> 00:40:24.881
He's in a group chat

00:40:25.080 --> 00:40:26.961
with all the dealers.

00:40:27.680 --> 00:40:29.801
If this motorcycle
hasn't left the province,

00:40:29.801 --> 00:40:31.921
we could track it down.

00:40:32.480 --> 00:40:33.680
Perfect! Thanks.

00:40:34.680 --> 00:40:36.401
Since you're here, stay for a meal.

00:40:36.480 --> 00:40:37.721
I'm working.

00:40:38.801 --> 00:40:40.961
One meal won't hinder anything.

00:40:44.961 --> 00:40:46.640
What work? Delivering packages?

00:40:49.281 --> 00:40:50.881
Notify me once you get any leads.

00:40:51.000 --> 00:40:51.680
Thank you.

00:40:55.281 --> 00:40:56.680
Did you find anything on Chen Yumo?

00:41:05.680 --> 00:41:08.480
It's been years.
Stop wasting your effort.

00:41:11.120 --> 00:41:13.000
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

00:41:17.921 --> 00:41:20.000
Can't you see me right here?

00:42:02.600 --> 00:42:04.080
Did you dig up

00:42:04.080 --> 00:42:05.080
Dan Qing's background?

00:42:07.520 --> 00:42:08.480
It's all in here.

00:42:13.260 --> 00:42:15.820
(Profile of Dan Qing (Chen Yumo))

00:42:21.480 --> 00:42:22.281
Interesting.

00:42:24.721 --> 00:42:25.640
Interesting.

00:42:29.289 --> 00:42:32.782
♪Replacing the weight of tears
with that of sweat♪

00:42:36.576 --> 00:42:41.897
♪Covering the gunshot's sound
with wounds♪

00:42:43.970 --> 00:42:48.824
♪No one is born unyielding and strong♪

00:42:49.630 --> 00:42:52.777
♪But because someone
always rushes ahead♪

00:42:52.777 --> 00:42:55.881
♪To shield us from the storm♪

00:42:58.537 --> 00:43:03.671
♪When every extraordinary act
becomes routine♪

00:43:05.641 --> 00:43:11.273
♪Just to polish the badge
upon their shoulder♪

00:43:13.033 --> 00:43:16.617
♪Like light surging unseen
through the night♪

00:43:17.769 --> 00:43:25.209
♪Converging into your form♪

00:43:25.641 --> 00:43:28.319
♪Looking up♪

00:43:28.319 --> 00:43:31.858
♪Such dazzling glory♪

00:43:32.841 --> 00:43:35.401
♪Like hope♪

00:43:35.401 --> 00:43:39.334
♪Reaching out its arms♪

00:43:40.201 --> 00:43:42.853
♪Cloaked in light♪

00:43:42.853 --> 00:43:47.337
♪Alone, they charge ahead♪

00:43:47.337 --> 00:43:50.153
♪Traversing♪

00:43:50.153 --> 00:43:56.664
♪The battlefield of fate♪